  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2cbaeec8dbe84e069925173ac3a6210b, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dlg_Ruins_Totem_Shadow
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ElementalAlchemist.Dialogue.DialogueData
  _speaker: Ancient Totem
  _lines:
  - The last totem is faceless, and your reflection never appears upon it.
  - Marry the first light to the void that would swallow it. What is born is neither, only the shape that light leaves behind.
